Faqa<u>da</u>hunna sabAAa sam<u>a</u>w<u>a</u>tin fee yawmayni waaw<u>ha</u> fee kulli sam<u>a</u>in amrah<u>a</u> wazayyann<u>a</u> a<b>l</b>ssam<u>a</u>a a<b>l</b>dduny<u>a</u> bima<u>sa</u>bee<u>h</u>a wa<u>h</u>if<i><u>th</u></i>an <u>tha</u>lika taqdeeru alAAazeezi alAAaleem<b>i</b>
