Waamm<u>a</u> thamoodu fahadayn<u>a</u>hum fa<b>i</b>sta<u>h</u>abboo alAAam<u>a</u> AAal<u>a</u> alhud<u>a</u> faakha<u>th</u>athum <u>sa</u>AAiqatu alAAa<u>tha</u>bi alhooni bim<u>a</u> k<u>a</u>noo yaksiboon<b>a</b>
Wanajjayn<u>a</u> alla<u>th</u>eena <u>a</u>manoo wak<u>a</u>noo yattaqoon<b>a</b>
