Wam<u>a</u> kuntum tastatiroona an yashhada AAalaykum samAAukum wal<u>a</u> ab<u>sa</u>rukum wal<u>a</u> juloodukum wal<u>a</u>kin <i><u>th</u></i>anantum anna All<u>a</u>ha l<u>a</u> yaAAlamu katheeran mimm<u>a</u> taAAmaloon<b>a</b>
Wa<u>tha</u>likum <i><u>th</u></i>annukumu alla<u>th</u>ee <i><u>th</u></i>anantum birabbikum ard<u>a</u>kum faa<u>s</u>ba<u>h</u>tum mina alkh<u>a</u>sireen<b>a</b>
